data.title: Charlie Clark Nissan in El Paso I Your Hometown Nissan Dealership
data.meta_description: Charlie Clark Nissan is proud to be your hometown source for all things Nissan. Whether you're interested in Nissan sales or Nissan service, we're here for you.
data.text:
Nissan Dealership in El Paso, TX

Our dealership opened in April of 2017 and is a state of the art facility called NREDI 2.0, which is Nissan’s newest dealership layout and was just rolled out to the auto industry in recent years. Located on the west side of El Paso, we are an El Paso Nissan dealership different than other Nisan dealerships in the El Paso and New Mexico region. We have a high commitment to providing Truly Exceptional Customer Service to everyone who sets foot in our store, whether for new car purchase, used car purchase or a service department visit, and promise to give you an experience like no other new car dealership in El Paso or Las Cruces. From the moment you walk in, you will immediately experience an atmosphere different than other new or used car dealerships with lively music playing at all times and amenities such as popcorn, purified alkaline water, coffee and pan dulce.

Charlie Clark believes very highly in serving and for that reason our dealership has a huge commitment to the El Paso community and frequently participate in many local events supporting many programs including education, entertainment, sports and donate as well to many other charitable organizations. We are proud to serve our community as much as we can and appreciate the huge growth and acceptance our dealership has seen in such a short period of time. We thank you for taking the time to learn about our El Paso Nissan dealership and we look forward to having the opportunity to serve you with all of your vehicle needs. Come see and live the Charlie Clark experience!

We understand that you rely on our website for the most accurate information and its our responsibility to deliver the correct information and answer any questions you may have. Please do not hesitate to contact us with any questions you may have. Our Charlie Clark Nissan El Paso Staff will gladly answer any questions, concerns or online inquiries in a timely fashion manner. We value your time and look forward in doing business with you!

Our mission is to pair the right person with the right car and to exceed expectations in customer service.
